Package model

Interface Storage

All Known Implementing Classes:
Condo, Condominium, CooperativeHome, DetachedHome, FarmHouse, Freehold, MobileHome, MultiLex, Residential, SemiDetached, StackedTownHouse, TownHouse, TripleDeckers, VacationHome
public interface Storage
Interface helps achieve Abstraction. The interface "java.model.Storage" forces implemented class(es) to include one getter method and one setter method related to number of locker storages in the property.
